{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"What is it about flying cars?"},{"time":4000,"text":"We've wanted to do this for about a hundred years."},{"time":7000,"text":"And there are historic attempts"},{"time":10000,"text":"that have had some level of technical success."},{"time":13000,"text":"But we haven't yet gotten to the point"},{"time":16000,"text":"where on your way here this morning"},{"time":18000,"text":"you see something that really, truly seamlessly integrates"},{"time":21000,"text":"the two-dimensional world that we're comfortable in"},{"time":24000,"text":"with the three-dimensional sky above us --"},{"time":26000,"text":"that, I don't know about you, but I really enjoy spending time in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":29000,"text":"We looked at the historical attempts that had been out there"},{"time":32000,"text":"and realized that, despite the fact"},{"time":34000,"text":"that we have a lot of modern innovations"},{"time":36000,"text":"to draw on today"},{"time":38000,"text":"that weren't available previously --"},{"time":40000,"text":"we have modern composite materials,"},{"time":42000,"text":"we have aircraft engines that get good fuel economy"},{"time":45000,"text":"and have better power-to-rate ratios than have ever been available,"},{"time":48000,"text":"we have glass cockpit avionics"},{"time":50000,"text":"that bring the information you need to fly"},{"time":52000,"text":"directly to you in the cockpit --"},{"time":54000,"text":"but without fundamentally addressing the problem from a different perspective,"},{"time":57000,"text":"we realized that we were going to be getting"},{"time":59000,"text":"the same result that people had been getting"},{"time":61000,"text":"for the last hundred years,"},{"time":63000,"text":"which isn't where we want to be right now."},{"time":65000,"text":"So instead of trying to make a car that can fly,"},{"time":69000,"text":"we decided to try to make a plane that could drive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":72000,"text":"And the result is the Terrafugia Transition."},{"time":75000,"text":"It's a two-seat, single-engine airplane"},{"time":77000,"text":"that works just like any other small airplane."},{"time":79000,"text":"You take off and land at a local airport."},{"time":81000,"text":"Then once you're on the ground,"},{"time":83000,"text":"you fold up the wings, drive it home,"},{"time":85000,"text":"park it in your garage."},{"time":87000,"text":"And it works."},{"time":89000,"text":"After two years of an innovative design and construction process,"},{"time":92000,"text":"the proof of concept made its public debut"},{"time":94000,"text":"in 2008."}]},{"cues":[{"time":96000,"text":"Now like with anything"},{"time":98000,"text":"that's really different from the status quo,"},{"time":100000,"text":"it didn't always go so well testing that aircraft."},{"time":103000,"text":"And we discovered that it's a very good thing"},{"time":105000,"text":"that, when you go home with something that's been broken,"},{"time":108000,"text":"you've actually learned a lot more"},{"time":110000,"text":"than when you managed to tick off all of your test objectives"},{"time":112000,"text":"the first time through."},{"time":114000,"text":"Still, we very much wanted to see"},{"time":116000,"text":"the aircraft that we'd all helped build"},{"time":118000,"text":"in the air, off the ground,"},{"time":120000,"text":"like it was supposed to be."},{"time":122000,"text":"And on our third high-speed testing deployment"},{"time":124000,"text":"on a bitter cold morning in upstate New York,"},{"time":126000,"text":"we got to do that for the first time."},{"time":129000,"text":"The picture behind me was snapped by the copilot in our chase aircraft"},{"time":132000,"text":"just moments after the wheels got off the ground for the first time."},{"time":135000,"text":"And we were all very flattered to see that image"},{"time":137000,"text":"become a symbol of accomplishing something"},{"time":139000,"text":"that people had thought was impossible"},{"time":141000,"text":"really the world over."}]},{"cues":[{"time":144000,"text":"The flight testing that followed that"},{"time":146000,"text":"was as basic and low-risk as we could make it,"},{"time":148000,"text":"but it still accomplished what we needed to"},{"time":150000,"text":"to take the program to the next step"},{"time":152000,"text":"and to gain the credibility that we needed"},{"time":154000,"text":"within our eventual market, the general aviation community,"},{"time":157000,"text":"and with the regulators"},{"time":159000,"text":"that govern the use of design of aircraft, particularly in the States."},{"time":162000,"text":"The FAA, about a year ago,"},{"time":164000,"text":"gave us an exemption for the Transition"},{"time":166000,"text":"to allow us to have an additional 110 lbs."},{"time":169000,"text":"within the light sport aircraft category."},{"time":171000,"text":"Now that doesn't sound like a lot, but it's very important,"},{"time":174000,"text":"because being able to deliver the Transition as a light sport aircraft"},{"time":177000,"text":"makes it simpler for us to certify it,"},{"time":179000,"text":"but it also makes it much easier"},{"time":181000,"text":"for you to learn how to fly it."},{"time":183000,"text":"A sport pilot can be certificated"},{"time":185000,"text":"in as little as 20 hours of flight time."},{"time":187000,"text":"And at 110 lbs.,"},{"time":189000,"text":"that's very important for solving the other side of the equation --"},{"time":192000,"text":"driving."}]},{"cues":[{"time":194000,"text":"It turns out that driving,"},{"time":196000,"text":"with its associated design implementation and regulatory hurdles,"},{"time":199000,"text":"is actually a harder problem to solve than flying."},{"time":202000,"text":"For those of us that spend most of our lives on the ground,"},{"time":204000,"text":"this may be counter-intuitive,"},{"time":206000,"text":"but driving has potholes, cobblestones,"},{"time":209000,"text":"pedestrians, other drivers"},{"time":211000,"text":"and a rather long and detailed list"},{"time":213000,"text":"of federal motor vehicle safety standards to contend with."},{"time":216000,"text":"Fortunately, necessity remains the mother of invention,"},{"time":219000,"text":"and a lot of the design work"},{"time":221000,"text":"that we're the most proud of with the aircraft"},{"time":223000,"text":"came out of solving the unique problems"},{"time":225000,"text":"of operating it on the ground --"},{"time":227000,"text":"everything from a continuously-variable transmission"},{"time":229000,"text":"and liquid-based cooling system"},{"time":231000,"text":"that allows us to use an aircraft engine"},{"time":233000,"text":"in stop-and-go traffic,"},{"time":235000,"text":"to a custom-designed gearbox"},{"time":237000,"text":"that powers either the propeller when you're flying or the wheels on the ground,"},{"time":240000,"text":"to the automated wing-folding mechanism that we'll see in a moment,"},{"time":242000,"text":"to crash safety features."},{"time":244000,"text":"We have a carbon fiber safety cage"},{"time":246000,"text":"that protects the occupants"},{"time":248000,"text":"for less than 10 percent of the weight of a traditional steel chassis in a car."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252000,"text":"Now this also, as good as it is, wasn't quite enough."},{"time":255000,"text":"The regulations for vehicles on the road"},{"time":257000,"text":"weren't written with an airplane in mind."},{"time":259000,"text":"So we did need a little bit of support"},{"time":261000,"text":"from the National Highway Traffic Safety Administration."},{"time":264000,"text":"Now you may have seen in the news recently,"},{"time":266000,"text":"they came through with us at the end of last month"},{"time":268000,"text":"with a few special exemptions"},{"time":270000,"text":"that will allow the Transition to be sold"},{"time":272000,"text":"in the same category as SUVs and light trucks."},{"time":274000,"text":"As a multi-purpose passenger vehicle,"},{"time":276000,"text":"it is now officially \"designed for occasional off-road use.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":279000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":281000,"text":"Now let's see it in action."},{"time":287000,"text":"You can see there the wings folded up just along the side of the plane."},{"time":290000,"text":"You're not powering the propeller, you're powering the wheels."},{"time":299000,"text":"And it is under seven feet tall,"},{"time":301000,"text":"so it will fit in a standard construction garage."},{"time":304000,"text":"And that's the automated wing-folding mechanism."},{"time":306000,"text":"That's real time."},{"time":308000,"text":"You just push a few buttons in the cockpit, and the wings come out."},{"time":311000,"text":"Once they're fully deployed,"},{"time":313000,"text":"there's a mechanical lock that goes into place,"},{"time":315000,"text":"again, from inside the cockpit."},{"time":317000,"text":"And they're now fully capable of handling"},{"time":319000,"text":"any of the loads you would see in flight --"},{"time":321000,"text":"just like putting down your convertible top."},{"time":326000,"text":"And you're all thinking what your neighbors would think of seeing that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":332000,"text":"(Video) Test Pilot: Until the vehicle flies,"},{"time":334000,"text":"75 percent of your risk is that first flight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":341000,"text":"Radio: It actually flew. Yes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":343000,"text":"Radio 2: That was gorgeous."}]},{"cues":[{"time":345000,"text":"Radio: What did you think of that?"},{"time":347000,"text":"That was beautiful from up here, I tell you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":352000,"text":"AMD: See, we're all exceedingly excited about that little bunny hop."},{"time":355000,"text":"And our test pilot gave us"},{"time":357000,"text":"the best feedback you can get from a test pilot after a first flight,"},{"time":360000,"text":"which was that it was \"remarkably unremarkable.\""},{"time":363000,"text":"He would go onto tell us"},{"time":365000,"text":"that the Transition had been the easiest airplane to land"},{"time":367000,"text":"that he'd flown in his entire 30-year career as a test pilot."},{"time":378000,"text":"So despite making something"},{"time":380000,"text":"that is seemingly revolutionary,"},{"time":382000,"text":"we really focused on doing"},{"time":384000,"text":"as little new as possible."},{"time":386000,"text":"We leverage a lot of technology from the state-of-the-art in general aviation"},{"time":389000,"text":"and from automotive racing."},{"time":391000,"text":"When we do have to do something truly out-of-the-box,"},{"time":393000,"text":"we use an incremental design, build, test, redesign cycle"},{"time":396000,"text":"that lets us reduce risk in baby steps."}]},{"cues":[{"time":398000,"text":"Now since we started Terrafugia about 6 years ago,"},{"time":400000,"text":"we've had a lot of those baby steps."},{"time":402000,"text":"We've gone from being three of us"},{"time":404000,"text":"working in the basement at MIT while we were still in graduate school"},{"time":407000,"text":"to about two-dozen of us"},{"time":409000,"text":"working in an initial production facility outside of Boston."},{"time":412000,"text":"We've had to overcome challenges"},{"time":414000,"text":"like keeping the weight below the light sport limit that I talked about,"},{"time":416000,"text":"figuring out how to politely respond"},{"time":418000,"text":"when a regulator tells you,"},{"time":420000,"text":"\"But that won't fit through a toll booth with the wings extended --"},{"time":423000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":426000,"text":"to all of the other associated durability and engineering issues"},{"time":428000,"text":"that we talked about on the ground."},{"time":430000,"text":"Still, if everything goes to our satisfaction"},{"time":433000,"text":"with the testing and construction"},{"time":435000,"text":"of the two production prototypes"},{"time":437000,"text":"that we're working on right now,"},{"time":439000,"text":"those first deliveries"},{"time":441000,"text":"to the, about a hundred, people who have reserved an airplane at this point"},{"time":443000,"text":"should begin at the end of next year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":445000,"text":"The Transition will cost in line with other small airplanes."},{"time":448000,"text":"And I'm certainly not out to replace your Chevy,"},{"time":451000,"text":"but I do think that the Transition should be your next airplane."},{"time":454000,"text":"Here's why."},{"time":456000,"text":"While nearly all of the commercial air travel in the world"},{"time":459000,"text":"goes through a relatively small number of large hub airports,"},{"time":462000,"text":"there is a huge underutilized resource out there."},{"time":465000,"text":"There are thousands of local airstrips"},{"time":467000,"text":"that don't see nearly as many aircraft operations a day as they could."},{"time":470000,"text":"On average, there's one within 20 to 30 miles"},{"time":473000,"text":"of wherever you are in the United States."},{"time":475000,"text":"The Transition gives you"},{"time":477000,"text":"a safer, more convenient and more fun way"},{"time":480000,"text":"of using this resource."}]},{"cues":[{"time":483000,"text":"For those of you who aren't yet pilots,"},{"time":485000,"text":"there's four main reasons why those of us who are"},{"time":487000,"text":"don't fly as much as we'd like to:"},{"time":489000,"text":"the weather, primarily,"},{"time":491000,"text":"cost, long door-to-door travel time"},{"time":493000,"text":"and mobility at your destination."},{"time":495000,"text":"Now, bad weather comes in,"},{"time":497000,"text":"just land, fold up the wings, drive home."},{"time":500000,"text":"Doesn't matter if it rains a little, you have a windshield wiper."},{"time":503000,"text":"Instead of paying to keep your airplane in a hanger,"},{"time":505000,"text":"park it in your garage."},{"time":507000,"text":"And the unleaded automotive fuel that we use"},{"time":509000,"text":"is both cheaper and better for the environment"},{"time":511000,"text":"than traditional avgas."},{"time":513000,"text":"Door-to-door travel time is reduced,"},{"time":516000,"text":"because now, instead of lugging bags, finding a parking space,"},{"time":519000,"text":"taking off your shoes or pulling your airplane out of the hanger,"},{"time":522000,"text":"you're now just spending that time getting to where you want to go."},{"time":525000,"text":"And mobility to your destination is clearly solved."},{"time":528000,"text":"Just fold up the wings and keep going."}]},{"cues":[{"time":530000,"text":"The Transition simultaneously expands our horizons"},{"time":533000,"text":"while making the world a smaller, more accessible place."},{"time":536000,"text":"It also continues to be a fabulous adventure."},{"time":539000,"text":"I hope you'll each take a moment"},{"time":541000,"text":"to think about how you could use something like this"},{"time":544000,"text":"to give yourself more access to your own world,"},{"time":546000,"text":"and to make your own travel more convenient and more fun."}]},{"cues":[{"time":549000,"text":"Thank you for giving me the opportunity to share it with you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":552000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}